    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">In your time of need, you call upon a spirit of your school to help you. The spirit might manifest as a famous graduate of your school, your school&rsquo;s mascot, your school&rsquo;s symbol, or just the specter of a terrifying professor; regardless, the spirit&rsquo;s ghostly appearance demoralizes your foes. Enemies who begin their turn within the effect or who enter it must succeed at a Will saving throw or be @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.nywSVEeDvp1bk7L3]{Shaken} for 1 minute.</span></p>",
